    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（芸能事務所のマネージャーという仕事柄）\n（俺は、とある俳優さんの結婚式の二次会に招待された）",
      "startTime": 3.9275804646,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4739.086202099999,
          "startTime": 8.6666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 8.4950110753
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_01-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "……あら\n{user}さんも招待されてたんですね",
      "startTime": 9.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_01-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "会場が広くて気付きませんでした\n……休日にまで貴方に会うとは思いませんでしたけど",
      "startTime": 16.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 20.4506344159
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "いえいえ、こちらこそ全然気付かず……\nそれにしても凄い人数ですね、それも芸能関係者ばかり",
      "startTime": 23.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_01-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "人気俳優と、この業界でも有名な\n元マネージャーとの結婚式ですからね",
      "startTime": 33.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 36.0634006818
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_01-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "その二人が、仕事関係をまとめて招待したみたいですし\n人が多いのは仕方ないです",
      "startTime": 39.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 42.0331512452
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_01-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、対外的には一般人ということになってますけど",
      "startTime": 42.0331512452,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "対外的にも何も、マネージャーは一般人ですよ……\nmihoさんはどういったご縁で招待が？",
      "startTime": 51.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_01-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "プレタポルテの頃に、少し付き合いがありまして\nfranとkanaとまとめて招待されました",
      "startTime": 58.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.996733777
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_01-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "kanaはさっき、他の招待客と\n楽しそうに写真を撮っているのを見かけましたし",
      "startTime": 63.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_01-mhk008.m4a",
      "text": "franは……あの子のことですから\nつまみ食いだけして帰ったんじゃないでしょうか",
      "startTime": 71.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 73.6264164451
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_01-mhk009.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、いつも通りですよ\n……それで、{user}さんは？",
      "startTime": 76.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "それで……と言いますと",
      "startTime": 79.0382983847,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82.3126748088
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_01-mhk010.m4a",
      "text": "これだけ芸能関係者が集まってるんですから\n仕事の一つも取ってきたでしょう？　と聞いてるんです",
      "startTime": 85.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "ひぇっ……\nすみません、近くの人と挨拶するので精一杯でした！",
      "startTime": 90.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 94.6175042791
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_01-mhk011.m4a",
      "text": "今日の新郎は、マネージャー時代から有名でしたけど\n貴方とは大違いですね",
      "startTime": 98.7118458937,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_01-mhk012.m4a",
      "text": "私は……昔の知り合いを数人見つけたので\n挨拶がてら、ひとまず話は振ってきました",
      "startTime": 104.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.2803833645
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "さすがでございます……で、でもほら\n結婚式ですし、新郎新婦を祝うのが第一ってことで……",
      "startTime": 111.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "いやぁ、新婦さん、幸せそうでしたよね\n元々お綺麗な方ですけど、ドレスがよく似合ってて",
      "startTime": 120.4209733196,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 124.9728544872
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_01-mhk013.m4a",
      "text": "……そうですね",
      "startTime": 124.9728544872,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "うちの事務所にも、ウエディングドレスを着る仕事が\n何件かきましたけど、みんな楽しそうにしてましたね",
      "startTime": 129.3333287556,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり特別なものなんでしょうし\n本物のウエディングドレスなら、もっと嬉しいのかなぁ",
      "startTime": 135.766662089,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 139.8911710858
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_01-mhk014.m4a",
      "text": "さぁ……そんなものは、人によると思いますけど",
      "startTime": 139.8911710858,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 144.4396063606
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "み、mihoさんは、ウエディングドレスには\nあまり興味はなさそうですね……",
      "startTime": 147.4920268575,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_01-mhk015.m4a",
      "text": "全くありませんね",
      "startTime": 150.1656605839,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 152.0035290439
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_01-mhk016.m4a",
      "text": "別に、綺麗なドレス自体は嫌いではないですよ\n花嫁というものに微塵も心が動かないだけです",
      "startTime": 156.6999954223,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 160.2435515761
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_01-mhk017.m4a",
      "text": "誰かと結婚して一緒に生活するなんて\n想像したこともありませんし",
      "startTime": 162.6333287556,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_01-mhk018.m4a",
      "text": "一人で十分やっていけてるんですから\nあえて他人と付き合う理由がありません",
      "startTime": 167.6333257038,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 170.363027036
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_01-mhk019.m4a",
      "text": "それに、マリッジブルーなんて言葉もあるくらいですし",
      "startTime": 170.363027036,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "マリッジブルー？\n聞いたことはあるんですけど、どういう意味でしたっけ",
      "startTime": 177.0333257038,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 181.3571992593
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_06_01-mhk020.m4a",
      "text": "結婚を決めたはいいものの、新生活への不安とか\nこの相手で良かったのか、などと思い悩むことですね",
      "startTime": 185.9333257038,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
